{"tid":1802201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一日藍絲 一世藍絲","createTime":"2019-12-29T09:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T09:24:38.000Z","uid":264614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be0f2e7c1885abff91f45850fe9ccfd1acfda2c7","tid":1802201,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />訓撚醒未？<br />\n<br />\n呢條片相信好多人都睇左<br />\n未睇既快d禁入去睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GAIBXIvNbic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGAIBXIvNbic&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9wbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=80d9533a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GAIBXIvNbic</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片除左好有實驗性之外<br />\n亦都帶出左一個好重要既重點<br />\n<br />\n就係<span style=\"color: gold;\">藍絲測謊機</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正正常常入餐廳食肆或者其他鋪頭<br />\n你問人地黃定藍<br />\n我諗人地都唔會答你<br />\n就算答左你既<br />\n你都唔知信唔信佢好<br />\n令到佢地真假難辨<br />\n<br />\n但片入面當d藍絲老闆<br />\n見到自己友<br />\n就好似食左吐真藥 <br />\n乜撚野都爆哂出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢老藍絲原形畢露<br />\n<br />\n雖然而家和你app已上線<br />\n但仍然好多店鋪藍黃未明<br />\n為擴大黃色經濟圈效益<br />\n避免手足中伏幫襯左d藍扮黃既鋪頭<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位都仿效片入面既做法<br />\n各自做返自己個條村<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後報上去<br />\n務求令到藍店從此係香港消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上 <br />\n<br />\n對家而家鐘意玩便衣狗<br />\n我地就以牙還牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每人都拎一張片入面既poster係身<br />\n令到佢地都覺得敵我難分<br />\n<br />\n就算俾狗搜身<br />\n我相信咁多位都可以秒速脫身<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"ca50fcf29fe558ce374473519e4e38d70b61d395","tid":1802201,"uid":264614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:23:24.000Z","msg":"請大家謹記 長玩長有 先係我地既重點"},{"pid":"61004ec134b652a54db2f1dfae9fcbba7585c617","tid":1802201,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"根本真黃既自己會表態<br />\n唔表態既一係藍一係港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事實係即使區選嬴左其實社會上大多數人唔係藍就係豬<br />\n難道你覺得成左年但票都唔撚投果班人會係黃？<br />\n頂盡只係唔深藍但一定係淺藍/死港豬"}]}